        "text": "Hmm realy really interesting he basically is pointing to larger issues of \"sustainability\" of this whole thing one might call programming (industrial?) culture. People need to care about things in a specific manner to sustain such a thing. In some sense its a cultural thing. The Hyper Individualism of consumerism plays also a role here. Not sure yet what it means but it comes with big implications, very good observations of the zeitgeist.",
